  "detailed_description": "Tactical Operations Force - TOF is a Third Person Shooter Game that allow players to play up to 10 vs 10 matches over the internet on Steam.<br />\r\nMain Game features are:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMultiplayer System<br />\r\nLAN Multiplayer System<br />\r\nSingle Player<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers are able to buy weapons with gamecoins that are obtained playing the game. The game have 4 different modes:<br />\r\nConquest<br />\r\nRush<br />\r\nTeam DeathMatch<br />\r\nDeathMatch<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame is under development and currently we are in Beta Stage, we are going to include more weapons, customization options and more maps in the near future.",
  "about_the_game": "Tactical Operations Force - TOF is a Third Person Shooter Game that allow players to play up to 10 vs 10 matches over the internet on Steam.<br />\r\nMain Game features are:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMultiplayer System<br />\r\nLAN Multiplayer System<br />\r\nSingle Player<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlayers are able to buy weapons with gamecoins that are obtained playing the game. The game have 4 different modes:<br />\r\nConquest<br />\r\nRush<br />\r\nTeam DeathMatch<br />\r\nDeathMatch<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame is under development and currently we are in Beta Stage, we are going to include more weapons, customization options and more maps in the near future.",
